text: Katrineholms VK is a volleyball club in the town of Katrineholm in Sweden. It was established on 30 March 1977 as a breakout out of KFUM Katrineholm's volleyball section. The club won the Swedish women's national championship in the years of 2010, 2011 and 2013 ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:Volleyball clubs in Sweden Category:1977 establishments in Sweden
